        "TileImage": "$($repository 07c64264-9fa9-4c4a-a933-802011bee9e6).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47. Today we have just two targets, and limited time, so lets get started. Salvatore Bravuoro. was a target last time who somehow survived your murder. I don&apos;t know how, but that&apos;s how it happened. Then we have Brother Akhram. He&apos;s a Moroccan tycoon who lives a luxurious life in Sapienza. We&apos;ll probably delve into his family later. He has been suspected of aggravated train robberies and street fights committed in his youth. Thats it 47. I will leave you to prepare. Have fun!",
